{"tid":229774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺中國人當子女只係工具","createTime":"2017-05-04T22:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T00:18:01.000Z","uid":49197,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a82409dc173664d3b221ae08ee81bcbd701384db","tid":229774,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T22:51:50.000Z","msg":"啱啱唸倒，中國底層家長好鐘意大庭廣眾為咗外人打罵子女，其實主要唔係因為自己覺得子女錯，而係純粹想做個樣，等子女得罪咗嘅人唔責難自己，咁自己就可以全身而退，唔洗負責任。<br />\n而上層社會既權貴家長就直頭完全偏袒子女，等佢地養成蝦蝦霸霸既性格<br />\n<br />\n總結而言，中國人只係當子女係一件工具，自己有權有勢既時候，子女就係自己彰顯權力既一件飾品，縱容佢地胡作非為；勢窮力弱之時，就會適當時候當佢地係棄子，用嚟祭旗。成日話中國人血濃於水，其實細心d唸，中國人先係最無情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300aef412e779a7ecad487b7975d3a3ed929da8a","tid":229774,"uid":106027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:26:57.000Z","msg":"點會係棄子 等緊佢地養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa23c4a62ace01f187bbc92f5fdd3e9273d85749","tid":229774,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:37:53.000Z","msg":"同老母講自己點樣儲緊錢等自己將來退休用，佢完全get唔到個concept <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:每個月俾緊8000家用"},{"pid":"5fdf0bae458a2c766efb05af60944e8404356ca7","tid":229774,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:39:51.000Z","msg":"其實唔係，反而香港人先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51dfd6547b5629b8474256e484d44d315d0e0b7","tid":229774,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:40:06.000Z","msg":"轉個角度<br />\n有部份子女咪一樣當父母係工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2785addb97629df2af1a9dd2279c679a28e2ff0","tid":229774,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T23:42:45.000Z","msg":"母親節打老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c203fb9985c061c16024fb41effaa2981a33ba1d","t